tosdr.case: Failure to enforce any provision of the Terms of Service does not constitute a waiver of such provision

title: Failure to enforce any provision of the Terms of Service does not constitute a waiver of such provision
quoteText: No waiver of any term of these Terms shall be deemed a further or continuing waiver of such term or any other term, and Pinterest's failure to assert any right or provision under these Terms shall not constitute a waiver of such right or provision.
